Package com.tome25.utils.logging

Class LoggingPrintStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.FilterOutputStream
        • java.io.PrintStream
          • com.tome25.utils.logging.LoggingPrintStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable
    public class LoggingPrintStream
extends PrintStream
    A PrintStream that writes everything to a Logger. Everything written into it after the last newline will be buffered until the next newline or flush.
    Author:
    ToMe25
